# Task Management Module
A robust module for managing tasks efficiently, with advanced features for organization, prioritization, and workflow customization.

## Core Features
Essential operations and properties for tasks, supporting all core interactions and requirements.

### Task CRUD Operations
- Create, read, update, and delete tasks
- Title (required), description, and notes fields
- Rich text editor for task descriptions
- Quick-add task input with keyboard shortcuts
- Bulk operations: mark multiple as complete, delete, reschedule

### Task Properties
- Due date and time with date picker
- Priority levels: Urgent, High, Normal, Low with color coding
- Status tracking: Not Started, In Progress, Completed, Archived
- Estimated duration (in minutes) for time tracking
- Custom tags for categorization (e.g., #work, #personal, #health)
- Task color customization for visual organization

### Task Organization
- Subtasks/checklists with progress indicators
- Task dependencies (blocking/blocked by relationships)
- Recurring tasks with patterns: daily, weekly, monthly, custom
- File attachments support (documents, images, PDFs)
- Task templates for repetitive workflows

## Views & Filtering
Multiple ways to view, sort, and filter tasks enable flexible task management and tailored perspectives.

- Multiple view modes: List, Kanban board, Table
- Smart filters: Today, Tomorrow, This Week, Overdue, No Due Date
- Custom saved filters by tags, categories, priority, status
- Search functionality across title, description, and notes
- Sort by: due date, priority, creation date, manual drag-and-drop order

## User Experience
Designed for speed, accessibility, and convenience with modern UI patterns and shortcuts.

- Drag-and-drop task reordering
- Inline editing for quick updates
- Keyboard shortcuts for power users
- Toast notifications for actions (created, completed, deleted)
- Undo/redo functionality for accidental deletions
